name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: ipc.[port_number].weighted-cost.handler
description:
The weight multiplier to apply to the time spent in the
    HANDLER phase which do not involve holding a lock.
    See org.apache.hadoop.ipc.ProcessingDetails.Timing for more details on
    this phase. This property applies to WeightedTimeCostProvider.

name: ipc.client.kill.max
description: Defines the maximum number of clients to disconnect in one go.

name: ha.health-monitor.connect-retry-interval.ms
description: How often to retry connecting to the service.

name: dfs.client.test.drop.namenode.response.number
description:
The number of Namenode responses dropped by DFSClient for each RPC call.  Used
    for testing the NN retry cache.

name: hadoop.zk.num-retries
description: Number of tries to connect to ZooKeeper.
